{"tid":246773,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"魚旦唔辣邊好食架？","createTime":"2017-05-17T09:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T18:48:49.000Z","uid":112919,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32bc8925425bb3dc49ba55e818e5425bcc0b3fda","tid":246773,"uid":112919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/172746_b22e0bb84712e97ef07f57ab679d7f9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F172746_b22e0bb84712e97ef07f57ab679d7f9c.jpg&h=c04df53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過油麻地站一定會食<strong>通達辣魚旦</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有邊間好食話過我知！"},{"pid":"80e51ec218d032897e5a2837cdce0087ec5851f8","tid":246773,"uid":22591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"油麻地陳記都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ba307277b9d079a39f8909f1948a8cb43f82a5","tid":246773,"uid":112919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油麻地陳記都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陳記都係靠啲醬汁咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n頭先醒起，尖東橋林昌記啲魚旦仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔靠醬汁，原本已經好有魚味，同個姐姐吹下水幾開心"},{"pid":"035cdedc6ca0a71aabba1acd6f53a06306938f22","tid":246773,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"紅磡陳記係用滾水浸熟魚蛋之後再淋汁落去,一啲都唔好食"},{"pid":"9f195c1a5beecc47e5f6470084bfc9589ce99cfa","tid":246773,"